                <h1>Understanding Background Music: Meaning and Importance</h1>
                <p>Background music refers to the instrumental sounds that play softly in the background of a scene or setting, enhancing the mood and atmosphere. It can evoke emotions, influence perceptions, and create a sense of immersion. Common in films, cafes, and events, it aids in storytelling or promotes relaxation without being distracting.</p>
